            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "港股開市︱初段再升 恒指漲123點報26971點 快手高開近2%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股開市初段持續向好，恒生指數開市報26971點，升123點或0.46%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數開報5894點，升24點或0.42%；國企指數以9328點開市，升42點或0.46%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股6.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股6.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">個別股份方面，快手(01024)官宣擬發美元及人民幣優先票據，該股今早開報80元，升1.98%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">京東物流(02618)擬變相私有化德邦股份(603056.SH)，料涉資約37.97億元人民幣；該股今早開報11.8元，跌0.17%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240509_FI_source-web_01024-3.jpg.webp\">\n<img src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240509_FI_source-web_01024-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">重磅股普遍造好，阿里巴巴(09988)開報163.8元，升2.44%；騰訊(00700)開報634元，升1.04%；美團(03690)開報104.9元，暫時無升跌。滙控(00005)開報127元，升0.48%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15580535-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e9%96%8b%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%88%9d%e6%ae%b5%e5%86%8d%e5%8d%87-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e6%bc%b2123%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b126971%e9%bb%9e-%e5%bf%ab%e6%89%8b%e9%ab%98%e9%96%8b%e8%bf%912",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-14 09:30:40",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "即月期指開報26900點 高水52點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指開報26900點，較上日現貨收市價26848點高水51點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月科指期貨開報5898點，高水28點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月國指期貨開報9301點，高水15點。</p>\n</div>",
